## MCP Servers

| Server | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `python` | Executes AT code via Python executor |
| `workspace` | Artifact gallery, plots, memory |
| `accelpapers` | Accelerator physics literature search |

## Requirements

- Python 3.11+
- Osprey framework with `[lattice]` extra
- No control system hardware required
